node.text:
An Absolute Crazy Spec On This Bugatti Divo 😍🔥
Photo @keystothejungle 

#bugattidivo

Start Your Engines. @jacobandco 🔥

The BUGATTI Chiron Tourbillon recreates the famous BUGATTI W16 engine in a timepiece. Visible from the top and through the BUGATTI horseshoe grilI, the animation and the inclined tourbillon are perfectly positioned to share this amazing movement with your friends.

The @jacobandco . Bugatti Chiron timepieces come with an exclusive "Swiss" passport. This bright red official document, available in multiple languages, comes with a greeting from Jacob & Co. founder, Jacob Arabo, a certificate of authenticity, technical details, instructions on how to operate the watch, a "Swiss stamp" and most importantly, the Jacob & Co. stamp, allowing you to enter the world of audacious luxury "Inspired by the Impossible."

Isn’t that fascinating? 😍

#cars #car #carlifestyle #carsofinstagram #carswithoutlimits #supercar #supercars #hypercar #hypercars

Feel all the power, energy and speed of the Bugatti Chiron on your luxury watch! @jacobandco 🔥

The @JacobandCo . Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon is a timepiece designed to honor the Chiron hyper sportscar. The tonneau-shaped case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the animated "engine block," is intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine. This engine, which operates on demand, as well as the rest of the caliber, is completely visible under a massive sapphire crystal. There are several finishes for the sleek case, including the warm glow of traditional rose gold and the modern blue metallic finish of titanium.

How much horsepower is there? 😳
Via @shinmikeyin 

#Bugatti #Chiron #pagani #divo #horsepower #lamborghini #lambo #luxury #luxurylifestyle #carsofinstagram #carlifestyle #cars #car

What a Beauty 😍 @jacobandco 

BUGATTI Chiron Tourbillon Rose Gold has a 55mm-by-45mm case made of highly polished 18K rose gold. 😍 Its tonneau shape is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron hyper sports car, giving it a sleek, aerodynamic appearance.  Inside is a replica of the BUGATTI 16-cylinder engine visible through sapphire crystal. 💎

 In 2019, Bugatti and @JacobandCo . formed a long-term partnership to create unique timepieces. The Bugatti Chiron is one of those watches.
